# MAYA Architecture

## Overview

MAYA is an AI Sales Executive for Propify Brokerage Agency.

The goal of MAYA is to communicate with real estate leads through WhatsApp, qualify them, answer their questions, send official project files, handle objections, and help move them toward booking or purchasing.

This is Version 1 (MVP).

The architecture is intentionally simple to allow fast deployment and rapid improvement.

---

# Core Components

## GitHub

GitHub is the Brain of MAYA.

It contains:

- MAYA System Prompt
- Propify Sales Methodology
- Architecture Documentation
- AI Skills
- Business Rules
- Future Improvements

GitHub does NOT contain project marketing content.

---

## Google Drive

Google Drive is the Content Management System (CMS).

It contains:

- Project Bible
- Sales Playbook
- Brochures
- Master Plans
- Payment Plans
- Price Lists
- Images
- Videos
- Unit Plans

Google Drive is the only source for project documents.

---

## n8n

n8n is the automation engine.

Responsibilities:

- Receive WhatsApp messages.
- Read Meta Referral information.
- Detect the current project.
- Load project knowledge from Google Drive.
- Send the proper context to OpenAI.
- Retrieve requested files.
- Send files back to the customer.
- Save conversation history.

---

## OpenAI

OpenAI is responsible only for conversation.

Responsibilities:

- Understand customer messages.
- Follow the MAYA System Prompt.
- Use the Project Bible and Sales Playbook.
- Generate professional responses.
- Guide the customer through the sales conversation.

OpenAI is not the source of truth.

