Business Logic

→ GitHub

Project Content

→ Google Drive

Conversation

→ OpenAI

Automation

→ n8n

---

# Version 1 Scope

Version 1 supports:

- One project at a time.
- WhatsApp conversations.
- Google Drive knowledge.
- PDF and media delivery.
- Sales qualification.
- Objection handling.
- Human handoff when required.

Advanced recommendation engines, scoring systems, and additional AI components are intentionally postponed until after the MVP is running successfully.

---

# Design Philosophy

Keep the system simple.

Ship fast.

Improve continuously.

Every new feature must solve a real business problem before being added to the architecture.
